        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>reusable spacecraft [300220159], manned spacecraft [300233886], spacecraft [300212528], air and space transportation vehicles [300222210], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
